  "description": {
    "zh": "什——哦，是你啊。进来吧，别傻站着……我们的分红好像打水漂了……Luka 那个混蛋一直联系不上！我们甚至查不到封锁区外的情况……我在那边一点眼线都没有。\n\n要是根本就没有什么 USEC 基地呢？也许那个狗娘养的 Luka 根本就没带什么小队……看看我们，竟然一点都没怀疑。还有你，狗屁鹰眼……他妈的，真是见鬼了。\n\n好吧……我们根本他妈的不可能从这儿对付那帮王八蛋。等我先发完火再清醒过来之前，别指望我想出什么新计划。怎么，你想帮忙？那就先去弄点酒来吧……",
    "en": "Wha-- Oh, it's you. Come in, don't just stand there... We've lost our dividends, it seems... Luka's not getting in touch, the fucking bastard! We can't even check what's going on outside the cordon... I \ndon't have any eyes there.\n\nWhat if there was no USEC base in the first place? Maybe this fucker Luka doesn't even have a squad... And look at us, we didn't suspect a goddamn thing. And you, fucking eagle eye... Fuck's sake.\n\nOkay... There's no fucking way we're gonna get these cocksuckers from here. Until I'm pissed and then sober again, don't count on a new plan. What, you want to help? Bring some more booze, then..."
  },
